## Environment Variables
Create a `.env` file:

MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
SESSION_SECRET=your_session_secret
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3000


## Run Locally
```bash
npm install
node seed_user.js
node seed_appointments.js
npm start


Open:
http://localhost:3000


